{
  "video_id": "O4Og5tFNiaU",
  "title": "What do you want to be acknowledged for? Christopher Littlefield at TEDxBeirut",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 22140.0,
      "end_time": 24492.0,
      "text": "We love recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 24492.0,
      "end_time": 27581.0,
      "text": "but we suck at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 27581.0,
      "end_time": 29775.0,
      "text": "Whether we want to admit it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 29775.0,
      "end_time": 33548.0,
      "text": "recognition plays a huge role in our day-to-day lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 33548.0,
      "end_time": 35312.0,
      "text": "in our happiness, in our well-being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35312.0,
      "end_time": 38939.0,
      "text": "both at work and in our personal relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38939.0,
      "end_time": 40831.0,
      "text": "But the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40831.0,
      "end_time": 42596.0,
      "text": "We are horrible at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42596.0,
      "end_time": 45137.0,
      "text": "We are horrible about giving it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45137.0,
      "end_time": 49194.0,
      "text": "we suck at receiving it, myself included."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49194.0,
      "end_time": 52757.0,
      "text": "And the problem is, most of us don't even know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52757.0,
      "end_time": 55114.0,
      "text": "I had a rule for a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55114.0,
      "end_time": 59131.0,
      "text": "that no matter whoever I sat next to, on the plane or on the subway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59131.0,
      "end_time": 61280.0,
      "text": "even if they had earphones on or they were asleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61280.0,
      "end_time": 63481.0,
      "text": "I had to get their attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63481.0,
      "end_time": 65380.0,
      "text": "and I had to interview them."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65379.99999999999,
      "end_time": 67163.0,
      "text": "And my first question was always,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67163.0,
      "end_time": 71913.0,
      "text": "\"What makes a good acknowledgment or compliment by a boss or supervisor?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71913.0,
      "end_time": 73902.0,
      "text": "Once they realized I wasn't hitting on them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73902.0,
      "end_time": 77071.0,
      "text": "trying to sell them something or get them to join a cult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77071.0,
      "end_time": 80590.0,
      "text": "then they would open up and they would tell story after story"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80590.0,
      "end_time": 83428.0,
      "text": "of the boss who never recognized them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83428.0,
      "end_time": 86194.0,
      "text": "the parents whose approval they wanted to gain"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86194.0,
      "end_time": 89711.0,
      "text": "or the teacher who made a profound difference in their life."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89711.0,
      "end_time": 93993.0,
      "text": "365 of these interviews later"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93993.0,
      "end_time": 97896.0,
      "text": "I've come to understand one thing for sure:"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97896.0,
      "end_time": 99397.0,
      "text": "We are crazy. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99397.0,
      "end_time": 100610.0,
      "text": "We are!"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100610.0,
      "end_time": 104241.0,
      "text": "And our relationship to recognition is confusing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104241.0,
      "end_time": 107091.0,
      "text": "it doesn't make much sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107091.0,
      "end_time": 111044.0,
      "text": "For example, I interviewed my landlord when I lived in Boston."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111044.0,
      "end_time": 114612.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Cathy, what is your relationship to recognition?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114612.0,
      "end_time": 120054.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, I love recognition, but it makes me so uncomfortable.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120054.0,
      "end_time": 124985.0,
      "text": "Cathy explained, \"I was at my retirement party.\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124985.0,
      "end_time": 128413.0,
      "text": "Cathy worked at this organization for over 2 decades --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128413.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131969.0,
      "text": "\"All of my colleagues were telling stories and thanking me."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131969.0,
      "end_time": 137822.0,
      "text": "I loved it, but I was so embarrassed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 137822.0,
      "end_time": 142096.0,
      "text": "What I saw with Cathy is what I saw in nearly all of my interviews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 142096.0,
      "end_time": 143713.0,
      "text": "that the majority of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 143713.0,
      "end_time": 150214.0,
      "text": "have this often multi-sided conflicting relationship to recognition:"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150214.0,
      "end_time": 152763.0,
      "text": "I love it, but I get so embarrassed;"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 152763.0,
      "end_time": 154764.0,
      "text": "it motivates me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 154764.0,
      "end_time": 156940.0,
      "text": "but I worry I won't be able to produce the same result in the future;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 156940.0,
      "end_time": 159096.0,
      "text": "or I don't like recognition;"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159096.0,
      "end_time": 161065.0,
      "text": "or I don't need recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 161065.0,
      "end_time": 162393.0,
      "text": "But after asking a few questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 162393.0,
      "end_time": 165101.0,
      "text": "it always turns to, \"I'm not comfortable with recognition\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165101.0,
      "end_time": 169481.0,
      "text": "or \"I'm not supposed to need recognition.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169481.0,
      "end_time": 172497.0,
      "text": "So, I don't know about you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 172497.0,
      "end_time": 174614.0,
      "text": "but I always thought that recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174614.0,
      "end_time": 176879.0,
      "text": "was supposed to be something positive, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 176879.0,
      "end_time": 178697.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178697.0,
      "end_time": 181096.0,
      "text": "So, that's what doesn't make sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181096.0,
      "end_time": 183213.0,
      "text": "That's why we are crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183213.0,
      "end_time": 185692.0,
      "text": "Why, if this is supposed to be something positive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185692.0,
      "end_time": 189336.0,
      "text": "do we all have these conflicting relationships to it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189336.0,
      "end_time": 191024.0,
      "text": "So right after Cathy said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191024.0,
      "end_time": 193828.0,
      "text": "\"It makes me embarrassed,\" I immediately asked why."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193828.0,
      "end_time": 197246.0,
      "text": "Without skipping a beat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197246.0,
      "end_time": 201438.0,
      "text": "\"Fourth grade, school --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201438.0,
      "end_time": 210638.0,
      "text": "in the middle of class my teacher goes, 'Cathy stand up!'\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210638.0,
      "end_time": 212831.0,
      "text": "So Cathy slowly stands up."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212831.0,
      "end_time": 216808.0,
      "text": "\"Now everybody look at Cathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216808.0,
      "end_time": 219764.0,
      "text": "Now that is a perfect uniform."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219764.0,
      "end_time": 226814.0,
      "text": "All of your uniforms should look just like Cathy's.\" (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 226814.0,
      "end_time": 231662.0,
      "text": "Awkward! (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 231662.0,
      "end_time": 236791.0,
      "text": "We all have these past experiences or associations with recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 236791.0,
      "end_time": 240008.0,
      "text": "and it's these past experiences or associations"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 240008.0,
      "end_time": 244296.0,
      "text": "that dictate how we experience recognition right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244296.0,
      "end_time": 247214.0,
      "text": "Now I am not a psychiatrist"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 247214.0,
      "end_time": 249214.0,
      "text": "and we are not going to, I'm not going to go all Freud"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 249214.0,
      "end_time": 250897.0,
      "text": "and talk about our childhood traumas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 250897.0,
      "end_time": 252207.0,
      "text": "what happened to you in 5th grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 252207.0,
      "end_time": 257054.0,
      "text": "and what your mom said to you, and we are not going to talk about you."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 257053.99999999997,
      "end_time": 259696.99999999997,
      "text": "We are not going to talk about all our childhood traumas."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 259697.0,
      "end_time": 261998.0,
      "text": "But what I do want to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261998.0,
      "end_time": 263914.0,
      "text": "are some of the things that we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 263914.0,
      "end_time": 266046.0,
      "text": "to ourselves and to others"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 266046.0,
      "end_time": 269113.0,
      "text": "that keep these conflicting associations in place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 269113.0,
      "end_time": 273363.0,
      "text": "limiting our ability to effectively give and receive recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 273363.0,
      "end_time": 276103.0,
      "text": "and limiting our ability to actually get present"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 276103.0,
      "end_time": 279713.0,
      "text": "to our own accomplishments."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279713.0,
      "end_time": 282602.0,
      "text": "If you go back to Cathy's example --"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282602.0,
      "end_time": 287331.0,
      "text": "Can you see what Cathy's teacher did was not actually recognize her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 287331.0,
      "end_time": 290546.0,
      "text": "Okay, maybe her uniform was spotless;"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 290546.0,
      "end_time": 292315.0,
      "text": "it was perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292315.0,
      "end_time": 294746.0,
      "text": "But she wasn't actually recognizing Cathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 294746.0,
      "end_time": 300227.0,
      "text": "She was using Cathy to teach the other kids in class a lesson."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 300227.0,
      "end_time": 304274.0,
      "text": "That's not recognition; that's manipulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 304274.0,
      "end_time": 309606.0,
      "text": "I told you that my first question when I was doing interviews was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 309606.0,
      "end_time": 314113.0,
      "text": "\"What makes a good acknowledgment by a boss or supervisor?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 314113.0,
      "end_time": 318597.0,
      "text": "9 times out of 10, people didn't tell me what made a good acknowledgment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 318597.0,
      "end_time": 321222.0,
      "text": "but instead, what made a bad one."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 321222.0,
      "end_time": 325097.0,
      "text": "And I was able to establish several ineffective practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325097.0,
      "end_time": 327482.0,
      "text": "that actually break down trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 327482.0,
      "end_time": 330590.0,
      "text": "and actually hurt our relationships and our connection with others."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 330590.0,
      "end_time": 333797.0,
      "text": "And I want to start today by sharing three of them with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 333797.0,
      "end_time": 338727.0,
      "text": "Number 1: I hate it when my boss give me compliments"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 338727.0,
      "end_time": 342317.0,
      "text": "right before they ask for something. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342317.0,
      "end_time": 346455.0,
      "text": "Joe, habibi. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 346455.0,
      "end_time": 350726.0,
      "text": "You were an all star last week in that sales meeting. All star!"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 350726.0,
      "end_time": 353547.0,
      "text": "Can you get me this report by five?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 353547.0,
      "end_time": 357780.0,
      "text": "How many people have a boss or a friend who does that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 357780.0,
      "end_time": 360197.0,
      "text": "Yeah, by the way this is being recorded."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 360197.0,
      "end_time": 361480.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 361480.0,
      "end_time": 363205.0,
      "text": "Okay, now here is the real question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 363205.0,
      "end_time": 365911.0,
      "text": "How many of you do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365911.0,
      "end_time": 368866.0,
      "text": "Ah, less hands!"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 368866.0,
      "end_time": 371031.0,
      "text": "You are all liars! (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 371031.0,
      "end_time": 374238.0,
      "text": "'Cause you do this too."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 374238.0,
      "end_time": 378579.0,
      "text": "Mom, you are so pretty."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 378579.0,
      "end_time": 380330.0,
      "text": "I love you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 380330.0,
      "end_time": 382431.0,
      "text": "Can I have 5 dollars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 382431.0,
      "end_time": 384047.0,
      "text": "We all do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 384047.0,
      "end_time": 387246.0,
      "text": "Number 2, and by the way my mother's watching this."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 387246.0,
      "end_time": 389131.0,
      "text": "So mom that wasn't about you."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 389131.0,
      "end_time": 391851.0,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 391851.0,
      "end_time": 396620.0,
      "text": "Number 2: I hate it when my boss sandwiches feedback"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 396620.0,
      "end_time": 399724.0,
      "text": "or criticism between two compliments."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 399724.0,
      "end_time": 402642.0,
      "text": "Also known as sandwiching, less eloquently known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 402642.0,
      "end_time": 404883.0,
      "text": "excuse my language, as \"the shit sandwich\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 404883.0,
      "end_time": 406640.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 406640.0,
      "end_time": 410163.0,
      "text": "George, Rona, you are such an asset to our team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 410163.0,
      "end_time": 412673.0,
      "text": "but if you make a mistake like you did last week again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 412673.0,
      "end_time": 414685.0,
      "text": "we are going to have to let you go."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 414685.0,
      "end_time": 417224.0,
      "text": "But, we are really glad you are here, really, really!"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 417224.0,
      "end_time": 418175.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 418175.0,
      "end_time": 425005.0,
      "text": "Or -- you are a really great guy but I just want to be friends --"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 425005.0,
      "end_time": 426340.0,
      "text": "Hug?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 426340.0,
      "end_time": 433068.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 433068.0,
      "end_time": 441434.0,
      "text": "Any compliment followed by a \"but\" is not actually a compliment."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 441434.0,
      "end_time": 445430.0,
      "text": "The problem? We have actually been trained to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 445430.0,
      "end_time": 448131.0,
      "text": "This is a standard feedback model."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 448131.0,
      "end_time": 450472.0,
      "text": "If you go to any business school you are going to get taught this."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 450472.0,
      "end_time": 453013.0,
      "text": "When you get feedback you are going to just put it between the two sandwiches."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 453013.0,
      "end_time": 455330.0,
      "text": "And it's not always wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 455330.0,
      "end_time": 459297.0,
      "text": "if we actually mean the compliments on either end."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 459297.0,
      "end_time": 461918.0,
      "text": "But most of the time, we don't."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 461918.0,
      "end_time": 465180.0,
      "text": "We are using those to make ourselves feel more comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 465180.0,
      "end_time": 467030.0,
      "text": "Okay! Number 3:"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 467030.0,
      "end_time": 473343.0,
      "text": "This is what we do when other people are getting recognized and we are not."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 473343.0,
      "end_time": 476580.0,
      "text": "Imagine yourself at a staff meeting, at a family retreat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 476580.0,
      "end_time": 481746.0,
      "text": "and that other guy or girl are getting recognized and you are not."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 481746.0,
      "end_time": 485048.0,
      "text": "If we like them, we are happy for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 485048.0,
      "end_time": 488847.0,
      "text": "Jealous, but happy for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 488847.0,
      "end_time": 494562.0,
      "text": "But if not, we are nasty."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 494562.0,
      "end_time": 498482.0,
      "text": "Jerk, kiss-ass --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 498482.0,
      "end_time": 500815.0,
      "text": "You guys have seen him. He doesn't really do any work, does he?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 500815.0,
      "end_time": 502831.0,
      "text": "Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 502831.0,
      "end_time": 504130.0,
      "text": "Now here is the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 504130.0,
      "end_time": 506281.0,
      "text": "When you are getting publicly recognized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 506281.0,
      "end_time": 509830.0,
      "text": "what are you worrying people are thinking about you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 509830.0,
      "end_time": 513558.0,
      "text": "Similar? Usually it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 513558.0,
      "end_time": 516796.0,
      "text": "Before you judge, give people the benefit of the doubt."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 516796.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519182.00000000006,
      "text": "Plus, I think it's time to give up the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 519182.0,
      "end_time": 522706.0,
      "text": "that someone else's success is our failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 522706.0,
      "end_time": 524632.0,
      "text": "Because that's just made up!"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 524632.0,
      "end_time": 530391.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 530391.0,
      "end_time": 532889.0,
      "text": "Now, when we do these ineffective practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 532889.0,
      "end_time": 535370.0,
      "text": "we worry people are going to do them with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 535370.0,
      "end_time": 536877.0,
      "text": "And if you want to stop worrying about them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 536877.0,
      "end_time": 538885.0,
      "text": "you gotta stop doing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 538885.0,
      "end_time": 541218.0,
      "text": "So this is what we do to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 541218.0,
      "end_time": 546089.0,
      "text": "What I want to talk about now is one of the things we do to ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 546089.0,
      "end_time": 548897.0,
      "text": "So you know when you start a new project at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 548897.0,
      "end_time": 550661.0,
      "text": "or you set a new goal for yourself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 550661.0,
      "end_time": 552545.0,
      "text": "You get this idea in your mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 552545.0,
      "end_time": 555497.0,
      "text": "what that end result is going to look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 555497.0,
      "end_time": 557797.0,
      "text": "I'm going to organize an event and a thousand people"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 557797.0,
      "end_time": 560499.0,
      "text": "or a thousand two hundred people are gonna come."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 560499.0,
      "end_time": 563054.0,
      "text": "(Applause) Right? Go TEDx!"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 563054.0,
      "end_time": 566057.0,
      "text": "Okay!"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 566057.0,
      "end_time": 568456.0,
      "text": "And it's going to be extraordinary!"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 568456.0,
      "end_time": 571685.0,
      "text": "And then you produce a result."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 571685.0,
      "end_time": 573964.0,
      "text": "And say 800 people show up"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 573964.0,
      "end_time": 575274.0,
      "text": "and people are coming up to you saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 575274.0,
      "end_time": 578747.0,
      "text": "\"Thank you, that was such a cool event, that was amazing!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 578747.0,
      "end_time": 582551.0,
      "text": "But we don't hear it 'cause what are we focused on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582551.0,
      "end_time": 585822.0,
      "text": "We are focused on the gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 585822.0,
      "end_time": 588215.0,
      "text": "The gap between what we actually produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 588215.0,
      "end_time": 592363.0,
      "text": "and what we had in our mind that we are going to produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 592363.0,
      "end_time": 593764.0,
      "text": "And then when people are coming up to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 593764.0,
      "end_time": 597007.0,
      "text": "they are actually recognizing us for this result."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 597007.0,
      "end_time": 598796.0,
      "text": "That's what they are experiencing."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 598796.0,
      "end_time": 602204.0,
      "text": "But that little voice inside our head blocks out all those compliments"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 602204.0,
      "end_time": 606514.0,
      "text": "and it focuses on, \"Yeah well, 200 people didn't show up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 606514.0,
      "end_time": 610246.0,
      "text": "and you didn't do that, you didn't do that, yeah, yeah thanks for the compliment.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 610246.0,
      "end_time": 613364.0,
      "text": "Yap, but I didn't do that, and I didn't do that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 613364.0,
      "end_time": 616600.0,
      "text": "See it's really important to focus on the gap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 616600.0,
      "end_time": 619022.0,
      "text": "to pay attention to the gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 619022.0,
      "end_time": 621496.0,
      "text": "That's where we learn and that's where we develop."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 621496.0,
      "end_time": 623898.0,
      "text": "But if we only focus on the gap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 623898.0,
      "end_time": 627264.0,
      "text": "that's how we go crazy, and that's how we burn ourselves out"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 627264.0,
      "end_time": 629181.0,
      "text": "and the people around us out."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 629181.0,
      "end_time": 632264.0,
      "text": "So what's important is: Before you look at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 632264.0,
      "end_time": 634315.0,
      "text": "stop and look here."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 634315.0,
      "end_time": 636868.0,
      "text": "Look at what you did accomplish and all the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 636868.0,
      "end_time": 639440.0,
      "text": "and the ups and downs you went through to produce this result."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 639440.0,
      "end_time": 641847.0,
      "text": "'Cause that's what gets us present to our motivation"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 641847.0,
      "end_time": 643803.0,
      "text": "and that's what gets us present to the passion"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 643803.0,
      "end_time": 646850.0,
      "text": "that helps us overcome the gap the next time."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 646850.0,
      "end_time": 648266.0,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 648266.0,
      "end_time": 653380.0,
      "text": "So, this is what we do to ourselves and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 653380.0,
      "end_time": 656487.0,
      "text": "And because we've been trained to focus on the gap our whole life"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 656487.0,
      "end_time": 658136.0,
      "text": "and not hearing what people are saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 658136.0,
      "end_time": 661521.0,
      "text": "or because of these ineffective practices that people are using,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 661521.0,
      "end_time": 665777.0,
      "text": "and also because of these past associations, the craziness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 665777.0,
      "end_time": 668182.0,
      "text": "I found that we've actually established"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 668182.0,
      "end_time": 672938.0,
      "text": "this sort of conditioned response to recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 672938.0,
      "end_time": 676532.0,
      "text": "Like Pavlov's dogs, when the bell was ringing they would salivate;"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 676532.0,
      "end_time": 680023.0,
      "text": "someone gives us a compliment and -- \"It was nothing!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 680023.0,
      "end_time": 685547.0,
      "text": "\"It was nothing! I swear!\" or, \"Voila\" or, \"It was a team effort.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 685547.0,
      "end_time": 691537.0,
      "text": "And maybe it was a team effort, but, but -- Here is my but, okay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 691537.0,
      "end_time": 695370.0,
      "text": "Maybe it was a team effort, but that's not accepting the compliment."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 695370.0,
      "end_time": 698546.0,
      "text": "We quickly divert the recognition away."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 698546.0,
      "end_time": 700398.0,
      "text": "We also make jokes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 700398.0,
      "end_time": 702131.0,
      "text": "or we play compliment ping-pong:"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 702131.0,
      "end_time": 704635.0,
      "text": "I love your dress! I love your shoes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 704635.0,
      "end_time": 710220.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 710220.0,
      "end_time": 713380.0,
      "text": "And sometimes it's even culturally institutionalized."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 713380.0,
      "end_time": 715580.0,
      "text": "Someone told me recently that in certain parts of China"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 715580.0,
      "end_time": 718946.0,
      "text": "it's actually considered impolite to accept a compliment."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 718946.0,
      "end_time": 721196.0,
      "text": "And also we find it in language."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 721196.0,
      "end_time": 724496.0,
      "text": "In French I say, \"Merci,\" and you respond with --"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 724496.0,
      "end_time": 725413.0,
      "text": "Audience: \"De rien!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 725413.0,
      "end_time": 728281.0,
      "text": "Direct translation:€“ \"It's nothing!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 728281.0,
      "end_time": 733005.0,
      "text": "Diversion, okay, you see it in Spanish as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 733005.0,
      "end_time": 736647.0,
      "text": "But there's an impact when we divert recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 736647.0,
      "end_time": 738577.0,
      "text": "What most people don't realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 738577.0,
      "end_time": 740580.0,
      "text": "is that a compliment is oftentimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 740580.0,
      "end_time": 745241.0,
      "text": "more about the giver than it is about the receiver."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 745241.0,
      "end_time": 750696.0,
      "text": "And when someone offers us a compliment, it's like they are offering us a gift."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 750696.0,
      "end_time": 752104.0,
      "text": "And when we divert it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 752104.0,
      "end_time": 756613.0,
      "text": "it's like we are taking that gift and throwing it back in their face."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 756613.0,
      "end_time": 758678.0,
      "text": "So even if you don't like it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 758678.0,
      "end_time": 761847.0,
      "text": "even if you don't agree with it, just say, \"Thank you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 761847.0,
      "end_time": 765933.0,
      "text": "And if it made a difference, let them know."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 765933.0,
      "end_time": 768930.0,
      "text": "My friend Carol told me a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 768930.0,
      "end_time": 770679.0,
      "text": "She said, \"When I was in fourth grade --"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 770679.0,
      "end_time": 772030.0,
      "text": "and by the way I don't know why everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 772030.0,
      "end_time": 773651.0,
      "text": "seems to happen in fourth grade, but it does."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 773651.0,
      "end_time": 775071.0,
      "text": "We should look at that."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 775071.0,
      "end_time": 776662.0,
      "text": "Marge, you can talk about that one, okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 776662.0,
      "end_time": 778292.0,
      "text": "Tell me what happens in fourth grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 778292.0,
      "end_time": 782104.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 782104.0,
      "end_time": 784014.0,
      "text": "She said, \"When I was in fourth grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 784014.0,
      "end_time": 787211.0,
      "text": "right before going on maternity leave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 787211.0,
      "end_time": 791169.0,
      "text": "my teacher Mrs McKay-Hill came up to me and she says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 791169.0,
      "end_time": 795141.0,
      "text": "'Carol, you know you are a really great student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 795141.0,
      "end_time": 796741.0,
      "text": "you know you are going to be okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 796741.0,
      "end_time": 798746.0,
      "text": "you are going to do great things.'\""
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 798746.0,
      "end_time": 802815.0,
      "text": "Carol said, \"I don't know what it was about what she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 802815.0,
      "end_time": 808130.0,
      "text": "but I went from being shy and reserved, to taking on sports,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 808130.0,
      "end_time": 811800.0,
      "text": "taking on AP classes, and just going for it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 811800.0,
      "end_time": 815019.0,
      "text": "And she goes, \"That compliment made such a huge difference in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 815019.0,
      "end_time": 817923.0,
      "text": "I never get to thank her for it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 817923.0,
      "end_time": 820569.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"Great! When you gonna thank her?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 820569.0,
      "end_time": 824557.0,
      "text": "She goes, \"I'm 44! That was 35 years ago!"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 824557.0,
      "end_time": 827684.0,
      "text": "I don't even know if she is still alive!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 827684.0,
      "end_time": 831502.0,
      "text": "That Friday, Carol was able to have an email forwarded"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 831502.0,
      "end_time": 834862.0,
      "text": "through the school department to Mrs McKay-Hill."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 834862.0,
      "end_time": 838198.0,
      "text": "And within hours she had a response,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 838198.0,
      "end_time": 842399.0,
      "text": "\"Carol, I worked in a lot of different schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 842399.0,
      "end_time": 843837.0,
      "text": "but I think I remember you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 843837.0,
      "end_time": 845958.0,
      "text": "I think you were in one of my fourth grade classes."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 845958.0,
      "end_time": 849578.0,
      "text": "How are you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 849578.0,
      "end_time": 851930.0,
      "text": "Carol immediately responded and told Mrs McKay-Hill"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 851930.0,
      "end_time": 854196.0,
      "text": "about the difference she had made in her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 854196.0,
      "end_time": 856965.0,
      "text": "Mrs McKay-Hill wrote her right back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 856965.0,
      "end_time": 860519.0,
      "text": "\"Carol, you know I grew up in a poor family"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 860519.0,
      "end_time": 863764.0,
      "text": "and I never thought I could go to college."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 863764.0,
      "end_time": 868889.0,
      "text": "But my guidance counsellor Mr Tingman told me I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 868889.0,
      "end_time": 872130.0,
      "text": "And I did and I became a teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 872130.0,
      "end_time": 874175.0,
      "text": "and I never got to thank him for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 874175.0,
      "end_time": 876363.0,
      "text": "I know he's passed away now."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 876363.0,
      "end_time": 878263.0,
      "text": "But I know where his kids are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 878263.0,
      "end_time": 880232.0,
      "text": "so I'm going go thank them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 880232.0,
      "end_time": 889080.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 889080.0,
      "end_time": 896294.0,
      "text": "There is a huge power in acknowledgment, recognition and praise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 896294.0,
      "end_time": 899297.0,
      "text": "but because we are often uncomfortable with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 899297.0,
      "end_time": 900565.0,
      "text": "we avoid it."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 900565.0,
      "end_time": 904615.0,
      "text": "And when we avoid it, we rob ourselves and others of the benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 904615.0,
      "end_time": 907769.0,
      "text": "that it brings, and we need to get better at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 907769.0,
      "end_time": 911366.0,
      "text": "We need to rethink our relationship to recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 911366.0,
      "end_time": 913946.0,
      "text": "We can start by looking at our own experience of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 913946.0,
      "end_time": 916246.0,
      "text": "our own relationship to recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 916246.0,
      "end_time": 918261.0,
      "text": "and being aware of these ineffective practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 918261.0,
      "end_time": 919697.0,
      "text": "that I shared with you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 919697.0,
      "end_time": 922763.0,
      "text": "and work on phasing them out of our daily use."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 922763.0,
      "end_time": 926437.0,
      "text": "We can also make sure that recognition doesn't just happen once a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 926437.0,
      "end_time": 929531.0,
      "text": "in our performance review or on our birthdays."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 929531.0,
      "end_time": 930681.0,
      "text": "That doesn't work!"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 930681.0,
      "end_time": 933297.0,
      "text": "No one should go one day at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 933297.0,
      "end_time": 936447.0,
      "text": "feeling like that what they do doesn't matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 936447.0,
      "end_time": 941214.0,
      "text": "And we do this by creating opportunities for recognition in our staff meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 941214.0,
      "end_time": 945341.0,
      "text": "in our daily conversations with friends and family."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 945341.0,
      "end_time": 948454.0,
      "text": "And by the way, this is not just when you are happy and inspired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 948454.0,
      "end_time": 952133.0,
      "text": "with the people you like to -- with the people you are frustrated with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 952133.0,
      "end_time": 953923.0,
      "text": "on the days when you are pissed off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 953923.0,
      "end_time": 956625.0,
      "text": "you are angry and you don't wanna go to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 956625.0,
      "end_time": 958163.0,
      "text": "That's the day to do it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 958163.0,
      "end_time": 960238.0,
      "text": "'Cause that's when it makes the biggest difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 960238.0,
      "end_time": 963019.0,
      "text": "And I wanna leave you today with one thing you can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 963019.0,
      "end_time": 964881.0,
      "text": "on the break here at TEDx"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 964881.0,
      "end_time": 966547.0,
      "text": "or when you are watching this."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 966547.0,
      "end_time": 969563.0,
      "text": "Go out and ask one person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 969563.0,
      "end_time": 973880.0,
      "text": "\"What do you want to be acknowledged for?\" or, \"What are you proud of?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 973880.0,
      "end_time": 975344.0,
      "text": "And then --"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 975344.0,
      "end_time": 977187.0,
      "text": "And by the way, they are not going to hear it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 977187.0,
      "end_time": 978226.0,
      "text": "they are going to divert the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 978226.0,
      "end_time": 980497.0,
      "text": "they gonna think that you are weird and all that stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 980497.0,
      "end_time": 983211.0,
      "text": "But ask them anyway and insist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 983211.0,
      "end_time": 987402.0,
      "text": "\"No seriously, what do you want to be acknowledged for?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 987402.0,
      "end_time": 989096.0,
      "text": "And then listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 989096.0,
      "end_time": 991631.0,
      "text": "And then ask them questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 991631.0,
      "end_time": 996194.0,
      "text": "about what it took for them to do what they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 996194.0,
      "end_time": 1000814.0,
      "text": "Because we usually don't want to be acknowledged for the result;"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1000810.0,
      "end_time": 1004418.0,
      "text": "usually we want to be acknowledged for all the ups and downs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1004420.0,
      "end_time": 1010520.0,
      "text": "the challenges and barriers that we went through to overcome that result."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1010520.0,
      "end_time": 1012982.0,
      "text": "Afterwards, just thank them"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1012980.0,
      "end_time": 1015212.0,
      "text": "and acknowledge them for what they shared."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1015220.0,
      "end_time": 1017724.0,
      "text": "And please, let me know how it goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1017720.0,
      "end_time": 1019312.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1019310.0,
      "end_time": 1029310.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}